title: T Commune
description: T馆, at 南山区华侨城创意文化园B3栋101, is a contemporary vegetarian restaurant focused on fresh and organic ingredients. It is located in Shenzhen's OCT art gallery district and is suitable for large parties and groups. Impressive presentation and daring flavor combinations. Cost is 200+ RMB per person.
streetAddress: 101, Building B3, OCT Loft, Nanshan District
